---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "الوثائق"
lang: "ar"
dir: "rtl"
---

<section class="docs-index">
  <div class="docs-inner">
    <h1 class="docs-title">الوثائق</h1>
    <p class="docs-intro">تصفح المصادر الأولية. انقر أي وثيقة لفتح العارض التفاعلي.</p>

    <div class="docs-grid">
      {% for d in documents.ar %}
      <article class="doc-card">
        <a class="doc-card__link" href="/ar/documents/{{ d.slug }}/">
          <div class="doc-card__thumb">
            {% if d.thumb %}
              <img src="{{ d.thumb }}" alt="{{ d.title }}">
            {% else %}
              <div class="doc-card__thumb--placeholder">PDF</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <h3 class="doc-card__title">{{ d.title }}</h3>
          <p class="doc-card__summary">{{ d.summary }}</p>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
